[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    372[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Continuous emergency screening:** The regex pattern set is run before any LLM invocation and routes to `handle_emergency_routing` with an IRB-approved emergency message that names 911 and 988. The conversation is paused (`terminate=True` in the finalized turn) and a `DISPOSITION_EMERGENCY_ROUTED` decision record is persisted. ✓
